[{"id":589299,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"如题，我朋友随手转发开车图，结果不小心转发到公司的工作群了，应该怎么办...","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589299","replies":82,"created_ts":1565004610,"created":"19:30:10","title":"不小心在公司的群开车了怎么办？","author":"Vneix","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Vneix","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f395/778f/242448_mini.png?m=1558164696"},{"id":589124,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1564687537","description":"<p>最近想开发一款小程序，既然重新挖坑，想着要不要上一个跨平台的开发框架。\nuniapp、taro，原生的，flutter。\n大家都在用哪个呢，说说优缺点呢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589124","replies":62,"created_ts":1564974727,"created":"11:12:07","title":"求推荐一个小程序开发框架， uniapp、taro 还是直接微信原生开撸","author":"gaigechunfeng","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/gaigechunfeng","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9786/b990/400557_mini.png?m=1564220717"},{"id":589239,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1562222718","description":"<p>3 年可还行?</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589239","replies":56,"created_ts":1564993357,"created":"16:22:37","title":"现在(2019 年 8 月), iPhone 6s (plus) 64G+还能再战几年?","author":"v2xeuser","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2xeuser","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bf07a96ee6f886e82c49f081f87b2c25?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589126,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1564689006","description":"<h1>播放视频的时候看不到时间！！！</h1>\n<p>不知不觉就刷了半小时，然后不知不觉的浪费了大好时光……</p>\n<p>~~PS：这不是迟到的理由……~~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589126","replies":54,"created_ts":1564974867,"created":"11:14:27","title":"我觉得抖音最变态的设计是……","author":"hotcool100","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hotcool100","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/621a8a44d017127e557353150cc1bd1c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589112,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"<p>是因为小米有专利？还是说仅仅是不愿意和小米一样？</p>\n<p>偶尔睡得晚了想第二天晚点起，就把闹钟设的晚一点，但是这可能导致下次需要早起的时候起晚，想到了一个比较沙雕的方法就是单独设置一个闹钟来提醒确认闹钟时间，但是事实证明这个方法不可靠，时间长了很容易无视这个闹钟顺手就把它划掉了...</p>\n<p>还有一种情况是比闹钟提前起来了，想把闹钟关掉，不然可能开车的时候闹钟就响了，但是不敢关，怕忘记打开导致第二天又没闹钟...</p>\n<p>华为论坛里这个反馈长期置顶，就是不肯做这个功能，到底是为什么？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589112","replies":54,"created_ts":1564973794,"created":"10:56:34","title":"为什么 EMUI 死活不肯加入“仅关闭一次闹钟”这个功能？","author":"dxgfalcongbit","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dxgfalcongbit","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/22a81e989318947f0ec56586a6253f40?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589083,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1564965562","description":"<p>好奇为什么这么多人选择 iTerm2，看了官网的介绍没找到有什么突出的特点，安装后的界面也并不简洁。</p>\n<p>iTerm2er 能介绍一下你是因为什么选择了 iTerm2 吗？</p>\n<p>我只是简单试用了 iTerm2，没被它吸引力影响到，我目前在用自带的 Terminal，配置如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>用 hammerspoon 给 Terminal.app 添加了全局快捷键 shift + cmd + e （ cmd + e 给 finder 了，为了与公司的 Win 机保持一致）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Termianl 自带的配置项和主题、自带的 tab 功能，自带的选择 /复制 /粘贴功能</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>默认的 bash，需要连续长时间使用时会切到 fish</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589083","replies":54,"created_ts":1564969982,"created":"09:53:02","title":"是什么让你选择了 iTerm2 ？自带的 Terminal 不好么？","author":"MrUser","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MrUser","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9ddd/9f66/329580_mini.png?m=1538202774"},{"id":589146,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"<p>lz 先前在北京工作了半年，得了干眼症，现在回了杭州。有段时间每天看电脑眼睛就难受，根本无法工作。这段时间好了点，但是眼角还是有白色液体，而且也不敢努力学习工作了。感觉这辈子都要安逸地过完。先前我还会晚上努力学习，现在都不敢用眼了。真的非常郁闷。有时候去逛干眼症吧，看到大多数人和我一样，用药也没用，折磨一辈子，真的是郁闷无比。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589146","replies":53,"created_ts":1564977361,"created":"11:56:01","title":"感觉干眼症好不了了，真的悲剧","author":"qiushui777","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/qiushui777","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3c09121de79b5443addc85d96fe2a943?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589237,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1564717604","description":"<p>公司最近变动很大，CTO 离职创业，新来的 CTO 是通过关系，被产品部负责人“安排”来的，所以现在整个技术部都归产品部管，需求也是来者不拒。</p>\n<p>新来的 CTO 之前只是一个小角色，完全不会管理，技术基础薄弱就算了...人品非常非常的不好，无论你说什么他都会怼回去，张口闭口自己以前的公司(一号店，点融)多厉害多厉害，你跟他汇报工作，他的反应从来都是，随便扔下一句话，比如我考虑考虑，或者我跟谁谁谁商量下，然后站起来就走(在回你话的同时，站起来就走)。特别不懂得尊重人，我偷偷找朋友去点融打听了一下，新来的 CTO 蔡某.. 之前一直都是有个大佬带着他，并不是凭技术入职的公司，为人也是心胸狭隘，情商不高，也不太出活，比较善于人和人之间的斗争... 后来也不知道为啥，可能带他的大佬给他画的饼没有实现，也可能画的饼不如来我目前的公司当 CTO 爽，就转投靠了我目前公司的产品部大佬。</p>\n<p>----背景介绍完毕</p>\n<p>我觉着继续待下去没意思，就提了离职，但是却被新 CTO 蔡某告知... 公司规定离职员工必须待满 30 天... 我百度大概搜了搜发现，他们这么做没啥不对，我自己只能待着受虐了,就是感觉很郁闷，真的不想在这里待了...</p>\n<p>想问一下大家，在这 30 天里，我可以只做交接和讲解，拒绝新任务和日常的活嘛？？ 扣工资什么的都可以接受的</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589237","replies":52,"created_ts":1564992933,"created":"16:15:33","title":"离职被要求必须待满 30 天","author":"survivors","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/survivors","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6528916c4fb1475b826976cf2aa4845c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589245,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1564965562","description":"<p>这两天刚装了 MacOS,第一次接触，发现里面很多细节的设计让人感动。\n想问下大家，该如何入门呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589245","replies":50,"created_ts":1564994386,"created":"16:39:46","title":"作为程序员， MacOS 让你觉得好用在哪里？","author":"alcoholpad","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/alcoholpad","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/65e686a5d3a0137493ebfb3bc4a472ab?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589099,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"<p>朋友弟弟被大学金融系录取了，咨询我 需要买笔记本电脑不</p>\n<p>这个我也不是很清楚，所以咨询一下 V 友</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>如果需要买电脑，要不要买配置高的，还是买个普通的电脑就好了~</p>\n<p>谢谢老铁们了~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589099","replies":50,"created_ts":1564971228,"created":"10:13:48","title":"大学金融系需要用笔记本电脑吗？","author":"justin2018","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/justin2018","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/83e8/4827/351542_mini.png?m=1547034280"},{"id":589063,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"<p>世界上居然存在一个地方，可以看视频，没什么广告，还可以评论，太神奇了<br/>\n不过问题是，youtube 这种推荐算法， 是你看了什么就给你推类似的，<br/>\n好像一道菜好吃，就让你使劲吃，吃到吐为止， 相当智障。<br/>\n所以请问下有没有什么优秀的频道推荐， 各种类型都行<br/>\n因为罗素说过： 参差多态乃是幸福之源</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589063","replies":50,"created_ts":1564967283,"created":"09:08:03","title":"youtube 上有什么优秀频道推荐","author":"dajj","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dajj","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3623/36f3/305915_mini.png?m=1552832586"},{"id":589060,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1564717604","description":"<p>工作内容是账号交易，账号安全这一块。</p>\n<p>这块怎么样？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589060","replies":50,"created_ts":1564966402,"created":"08:53:22","title":"知乎现在还值得去吗？","author":"leisurelylicht","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/leisurelylicht","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e50c/2bbb/115239_mini.png?m=1430818866"},{"id":589269,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1564687537","description":"<p>如题，经常遇到一些调用第三方 API 需要对数据处理问题，前后端总是分不清责任。以下是常见的三个问题</p>\n<ol>\n<li>字符串转换的问题，客户端需要显示“商家”，三方 API 返回 business，是否需要后端转换后返回呢？</li>\n<li>三方如 API 返回 A 和 B，客户端需要显示一个 C，C 的值为他们的平均值，是否需要后端计算后返回？</li>\n<li>搜索淘宝优惠券，需要过滤一些数据，假设淘宝会返回过期的优惠券，需要过滤掉，是否需要后端每次对搜索的结果进行过滤呢？</li>\n</ol>\n<p>有没有那一个标准文件指定过这些问题呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589269","replies":49,"created_ts":1564998031,"created":"17:40:31","title":"关于数据加工，前端后端责任讨论","author":"zero47","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zero47","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2c08a07b0bf31396809aba9065912964?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589138,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1564687537","description":"<p>突然发现 v2 首页有两个阿里招聘贴，并且都有提到 Facebook 开源的 GraphQL。</p>\n<p>阿里云 2020 校招内推，光速面试流程  <br/>\n（通过类 GraphQL+Serverless 实现接口聚合，减少前后端沟通成本）  <br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/587238\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/587238</a></p>\n<p>[阿里巴巴秋招] 飞猪用户技术，免笔试极速内推！可查进度  <br/>\n（参与端领域开源技术建设：Nodejs / Graphql / Serverless ）   <br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/588764\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/588764</a></p>\n<p>去年 Linux 基金会成立了 GraphQL 基金会，今年亚马逊 AWS 宣布加入   <br/>\n<a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/aws-joins-the-graphql-foundation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/aws-joins-the-graphql-foundation/</a></p>\n<p>掘金、简书 上也有频繁发布的大量 GraphQL 各种相关博客   <br/>\n<a href=\"https://juejin.im/tag/GraphQL\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://juejin.im/tag/GraphQL</a> <br/>\n<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/search?q=GraphQL\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.jianshu.com/search?q=GraphQL</a> <br/></p>\n<p>GitHub 上各种语言的开源实现都有了，Star 数基本都挺高。   <br/>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/search?q=graphql\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/search?q=graphql</a></p>\n<p>V 站、知乎、技术群等也有很多关于 GraphQL 的讨论，看起来 GraphQL 已经是一个大趋势了。   <br/>\n<a href=\"https://graphql.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://graphql.org/</a> <br/>\n<a href=\"https://graphql.cn/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://graphql.cn/</a> <br/>\n<a href=\"https://graphql.org.cn/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://graphql.org.cn/</a> <br/></p>\n<p>那么问题来了，都 9102 年了，大家有没有用上 Facebook 出的 GraphQL ？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589138","replies":46,"created_ts":1564976466,"created":"11:41:06","title":"都 9102 年了，大家有没有用上 Facebook 出的 GraphQL ？","author":"StarkWhite","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/StarkWhite","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/60fd165cf3ea72cee620e71475af652c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":589062,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1564402099","description":"<p><img alt=\"ecOm2d.png\" src=\"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/08/05/ecOm2d.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589062","replies":46,"created_ts":1564966963,"created":"09:02:43","title":"小白弱弱的问一句，这款 MacBook 能装 pubg 吃鸡吗","author":"zxq2233","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zxq2233","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/80be/120a/349056_mini.png?m=1550225698"},{"id":589208,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1558512651","description":"<p>缘由是 618 那天看到阿里云有促销，买了一台最基本配机器。</p>\n<p>然后那段时间也正好“英语”上头，所以就突发奇想在命令行里查单词多酷；后面搜到有几个可以这么操作的，但都是要安装，感觉为了查单词要安装个包，多余了点，就做了个无依赖的（你要是连 curl 都没有，我很怀疑你是不是目标用户）工具。</p>\n<p>比如你要查 cool 这个单词的时候：</p>\n<pre><code>curl v2en.co/cool\n</code></pre>\n<p>或者</p>\n<pre><code>curl v2en.co/凉爽的\n</code></pre>\n<p>要查词组的时候：</p>\n<pre><code>curl v2en.co/cool%20down\n</code></pre>\n<p>后面一位知友 ChaiFeng 改进了俺之前写的 bash function，如下：</p>\n<pre><code>v2() {\n  declare q=\"$*\"\n  curl --user-agent curl \"https://v2en.co/${q// /%20}\"\n}\n\nv2-sh() {\n  while echo -n \"v2en&gt; \"\n  read -r input\n  [[ -n \"$input\" ]]\n  do v2 \"$input\"\n  done\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>现在在命令行里，你就可以直接这样操作了：</p>\n<pre><code>$ v2 cool down\n╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n║   _____   ____    ____   _          _____    ____  __          __ _   _ \n║  / ____| / __ \\  / __ \\ | |        |  __ \\  / __ \\ \\ \\        / /| \\ | |\n║ | |     | |  | || |  | || |        | |  | || |  | | \\ \\  /\\  / / |  \\| |\n║ | |     | |  | || |  | || |        | |  | || |  | |  \\ \\/  \\/ /  | . ` |\n║ | |____ | |__| || |__| || |____    | |__| || |__| |   \\  /\\  /   | |\\  |\n║  \\_____| \\____/  \\____/ |______|   |_____/  \\____/     \\/  \\/    |_| \\_|\n║             