| \\_||_____| \\____/ |____/ |_____||______||_____|   |_|      |_|   \n║                                                                      \n║──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n║ 解释：\n║ 牛逼；牛 B\n║──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n║ Try curl v2en.co/:help for more commands.\n╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n</code></pre>\n<p>有用好玩欢迎安利给周围的朋友同事呀</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589208","replies":44,"created_ts":1564989433,"created":"15:17:13","title":"工程师装逼神器👨‍💻 - 命令行查单词工具","author":"hlwjia","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hlwjia","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/faba/96b3/271162_mini.png?m=1550832505"},{"id":589078,"node":"广州","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096","description":"最近爸妈催着买房。也跟着中介去看了一些。但是由于不是本地人有些问题想问下 v 友。<br />1.现在买萝岗板块是不是迟了，和增城 21 号线哪个更有发展空间。<br />2.由于我刚毕业银行流水不够，能用爸妈的流水担保嘛<br />3.公积金贷款是要六个月还是十二个月。网上好像有两种说法。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/589078","replies":44,"created_ts":1564969156,"created":"09:39:16","title":"[买房咨询] 广州哪个地段适合上车","author":"aichipipizhu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/aichipipizhu","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/978c/e79f/340755_mini.png?m=1546842097"}]